{"title_page": "Koki Hasegawa", "text_new": "{{short description|Japanese footballer}}\n{{Orphan|date=October 2017}}\n\n{{Infobox football biography\n|name=Koki Hasegawa\n|image=\n|image_size=\n|caption=\n|fullname=Koki Hasegawa\n|birth_date={{Birth date and age|1999|4|27}}\n|birth_place=[[Tokyo]], [[Japan]]\n|death_date=\n|death_place=\n|height={{Height|m=1.78}}\n|position=[[Defender (association football)|Defender]]\n|currentclub=[[FC Tokyo]]\n|clubnumber=49\n|youthyears1=|youthclubs1=[[FC Tokyo]]\n|years1=2017\u2013|clubs1=[[FC Tokyo]]|caps1=|goals1=\n|totalcaps=|totalgoals=\n|nationalyears1=|nationalteam1=|nationalcaps1=|nationalgoals1=\n|manageryears1=|managerclubs1=\n|medaltemplates=\n|club-update=\n|nationalteam-update=\n}}\n{{Nihongo|'''Koki Hasegawa'''|\u9577\u8c37\u5ddd \u5149\u57fa|Hasegawa Koki|born April 27, 1999}} is a [[Japanese people|Japanese]] [[Association football|football]] player.<ref>{{J.League player|23309}}</ref> He plays for [[FC Tokyo]].\n\n==Career==\nKoki Hasegawa joined [[J1 League]] club [[FC Tokyo]] in 2017.\n\n==References==\n{{Reflist}}\n\n==External links==\n*{{J.League player|23309}}\n\n{{DEFAULTSORT:Hasegawa, Koki}}\n[[Category:1999 births]]\n[[Category:Living people]]\n[[Category:Association football people from Tokyo]]\n[[Category:Japanese footballers]]\n[[Category:J1 League players]]\n[[Category:FC Tokyo players]]\n[[Category:Association football defenders]]\n\n\n{{Japan-footy-defender-1990s-stub}}\n", "text_old": "{{Orphan|date=October 2017}}\n\n{{Infobox football biography\n|name=Koki Hasegawa\n|image=\n|image_size=\n|caption=\n|fullname=Koki Hasegawa\n|birth_date={{Birth date and age|1999|4|27}}\n|birth_place=[[Tokyo]], [[Japan]]\n|death_date=\n|death_place=\n|height={{Height|m=1.78}}\n|position=[[Defender (association football)|Defender]]\n|currentclub=[[FC Tokyo]]\n|clubnumber=49\n|youthyears1=|youthclubs1=[[FC Tokyo]]\n|years1=2017\u2013|clubs1=[[FC Tokyo]]|caps1=|goals1=\n|totalcaps=|totalgoals=\n|nationalyears1=|nation